history.content: I got an offer to be a CS course tutor and student IT technician for work study. Which one is more preferable for a CS major? Will either of them help my resume? I think I would enjoy either position. I like teaching, but I also think I will learn something new as IT technician.
history.subject: CS Course Tutor vs. IT Technician
